_sText:
This is my first map in valve hammer editor (source sdk)
It is jail map, witch includes:

1 BIG JAIL and 4 OUTSIDE LOCATIONS

IN THE JAIL: 
Hospital, Obstacle course, ventilation system, armory, cells, disco, toilets, secrets

Disco has 3 normal songs and 1 special song!

OUTSIDE LOCATIONS: Spring, Summer, Autumn, Winter 

Spring: glock golf, shooting range
Summer: Pyramid with the tomb, pool, banana palms
Autumn: soccer, basket, lagoon, grave :-O
Winter: Beer Sauna and lot of snow

THERE IS A VENT. ROOM ON THE JAIL!!!

i hope, you like this map :)
Please share it with everybody!!! :D

PS: There are a lot of spawn points, but i dont know how many :D
PS2: Very special thanks too 3kliksphilip, for all his tutorials!
PS3: There are some secrets witch you must break to spawn a weapon!

( I am very sorry for my english, but i am from Czech Republic)
